channel.title: Project Dispatcher V2
channel.description:
[b]I will PM testers IP and port. If testers spread the IP, i will fucking hunt you down and rape you whatever sex you are[/b]
Hello people, If you old members heard of Shinscape (V2 or Isle), then it's back, yes! Now with a (cant tell) source, it's surely to be the (almost) best server yet!
I need testers!Quick! Post and you could test out the beta of Dispatcher V2 ;D
[size=20pt]Apply at Our forums for Coder Development Team [font=bip][url=http://dispatcher.smfforfree3.com/index.php]Here[/font][/size]
[b]Note : You have to register to view all boards.Apply at Development Team Board[/b]
[b]Testers : [/b] aerozero46 wouterscape Open Open Open
[b]Goals : [/b] - Mining (almost done) - Fletching - Cooking - Agility!! - Firemaking - Woodcutting - Herblore - Fishing - Specials - When all these are done, bigger starting point
[b]Already Done : [/b] - Runecrafting - Smithing - New starting point - Farming - Training slow - More shops - Portals
[b]~~~~ Pictures so far ~~~~[/b] [IMG]http://i188.photobucket.com/albums/z114/Shinsen_Soul/thjeving.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i188.photobucket.com/albums/z114/Shinsen_Soul/Smithingandstf.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i188.photobucket.com/albums/z114/Shinsen_Soul/Rc.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i188.photobucket.com/albums/z114/Shinsen_Soul/ssds.jpg[/img]
Testing anyone?
[size=5pt]Transformers Rock =P[/size]
[b]Credits : [/b]The person who coded LightSoul, Me , Fedexer and The guy who made Mopar coord list
